1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
After Cuiwei, the Empress says nothing. She's cutting losses.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
One pawn dies, send another. She'll never admit she planted demons.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Bloodline LV2. EXP 195/500. 305 to next level.

4
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Big gap. First — master what the python gave me.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Once, this was a killing banquet. Now, it's her training ground.

6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Frost Control.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Go.

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Not sharp enough yet.

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:44,000
One afternoon — from five scattered to ten on target. That's the Demon Progenitor's blood.

10
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:51,000
Next: ice wall.

11
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Defense — good enough. Holds an hour. No more fear of ranged attacks.

12
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:02,000
The python's dead — its books are mine. And they hide demon secrets.

13
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:09,000
So that's why I got Frost. But cross-attribute refining backlashes — for others.

14
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:15,000
Myriad-Demon Bloodline has no counter. Others' wall is my open road.

15
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:21,000
Tucked into the last page — not a technique. A way out.

16
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:28,000
Xuantian Pavilion hides the Calm-Heart Pill formula — it suppresses backlash. The python wanted in too.

17
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:35,000
To enter, I need the Emperor's trust. The border — a thousand-year tiger demon.
